{"tid":1966102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［峰迴路轉］原來係大陸人借臺灣IP鬧WHO","createTime":"2020-04-10T03:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T03:35:00.000Z","uid":259910,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"69c1304e25987e3537bcd7d37eabb1ffc0f0975a","tid":1966102,"uid":259910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:11:01.000Z","msg":"突發中心／台北報導<br />\n世界衛生組織秘書長譚德塞日前在記者會上，用3分鐘時間狂轟台灣，聲稱台灣對他進行各種人身攻擊、種族歧視等，而隨後竟傳出有網友以台灣名義向譚德塞道歉。對此，總統蔡英文及我國外交部都提出嚴厲抗議。另外，調查局也查出，這番言論竟是來自大陸網軍。對此，調查局將於10日上午11時召開記者會說明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 譚德塞狂轟：台灣霸凌我！竟爆出「大陸網軍」冒充台灣網友　調查局11點說明 | ETtoday社會新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 手機版 | ETtoday MobileWeb <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200410/1688154.htm#ixzz6JAxFk4Dv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200410%2F1688154.htm%23ixzz6JAxFk4Dv&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6xfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=05af04df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200410/1688154.htm#ixzz6JAxFk4Dv</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"abe71d4bccdd4162e0ecc9df329bb86effaa2322","tid":1966102,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蝗蟲禍害世界"},{"pid":"64cc8a8d3c32684630ddce95e5c3fad946c8a526","tid":1966102,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abe71d4bccdd4162e0ecc9df329bb86effaa2322","tid":1966102,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蝗蟲禍害世界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:14:41.000Z","msg":"借位一post，thx。<br />\n好多俾人深夜捉既人解救方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1966076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1966076</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3968ed102d7fbdd5495699d92a0dff59f2f206c9","tid":1966102,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r